data.description: This fully furnished, centrally located, creekside log cabin that is nestled in an established development boasts what vacationing in the Smoky Mountains is all about. This cabin can accommodate up to 6 guests while providing plenty of parking and an easy, well-paved drive to the cabin. No steep roads and only 10 minutes from the Pigeon Forge Parkway and only 5 minutes for the heart of Wears Valley. This community offers a pavilion, picnic area, a pool, and a peaceful river at the entrance. Walking in you will be greeted by well-maintained furniture and an open concept living room and kitchen area. This level has 1 of the 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The main level flows right onto the back, covered deck that backs up to a small creek and obtains the hottub. Upstairs, is the loft area packed with games and the additional bedroom and bathroom. This cabin is a great choice for a mountain adventure, relaxation, or a convenient break from the busy life. It's perfectly located, comfy, and surrounded by natural beauty. Video walk-through: https://youtu.be/H9tu5SExWls [Drone photography used]
